================================================================================
SPECIALIZED BRANCHES
================================================================================

This project includes three major specialized security branches:

1. Finance Security Branch
   - PCI DSS 4.0 Level 1 Compliant
   - AML/Sanctions Screening
   - Fraud Detection (ML-based)
   - HSM Integration

2. Healthcare Security Branch
   - HIPAA Compliant (Privacy, Security, Breach Notification)
   - FHIR R4 / HL7v2 Integration
   - PHI Protection
   - Medical Device Security

3. E-commerce Security Branch
   - Bot Protection & ATO Prevention
   - Payment Fraud Detection
   - Review Fraud Detection (NLP)
   - Marketplace Security

