PATENT NOTICE
================================================================================

This software includes implementations of:

- CRYSTALS-Kyber (NIST Post-Quantum Cryptography Standard)
- CRYSTALS-Dilithium (NIST Post-Quantum Digital Signature Standard)
- FALCON (NIST Post-Quantum Compact Signature)
- SPHINCS+ (NIST Post-Quantum Stateless Hash-Based Signature)

These implementations are provided for research and educational purposes.
